             were indicted for <rs id="t18320216-128-off711" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320216-128-off711" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320216-128-off711" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320216-128-cd712" type="crimeDate">23rd of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-128-off711 t18320216-128-cd712"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-128-off713 t18320216-128-cd712"></join>, 2 trusses of clover hay, value 6s.; 1 truss of hay, value 3s., and 1 sack, value 6d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320216-128-victim1106" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Walker
                        <interp inst="t18320216-128-victim1106" type="surname" value="Walker"></interp>
